column5: I've writen a few posts on this site about LacSeul Lodge. I type too slow to re do it but try Lac Seul on the search engine & you will probably find my handle. I just can't say enuf good about the resort. Great facilities,equppment Very friendly people & terrific fishing!If you can get in you will not be disapointed
One more thing, We are booked for May 25-June 1 & still have an opening for one more guy. Email me @ [email protected] if interested. We're Leaving from around Chi town
